# Track Log conventions

- Django API lives in `backend/trips/`; HOS logic only in `hos_engine.py`
- Never hardcode HOS limits in frontend — use API response
- Geocoding/routing in `routing.py`; respect Nominatim usage policy (User-Agent, rate limits)
- Daily log grid uses 15-minute quarters; four duty statuses per FMCSA paper form
- Property-carrying 70/8 assumptions unless docs updated
- Prefer free APIs: OSRM, Nominatim, OpenStreetMap tiles
